### Create Custom Tooltip Component - Recharts

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

Displays custom tooltip content when active, showing label, value from payload, page introduction text, and additional description. Returns empty fragment when inactive. Integrates with getIntroOfPage utility for dynamic content.

```javascript
export const CustomTooltip = ({ payload, label, active }) => {
  if (active) {
    return (
      <div className="custom-tooltip">
        <p className="label">{`${label} : ${payload[0].value}`}</p>
        <p className="intro">{getIntroOfPage(label)}</p>
        <p className="desc">Anything you want can be displayed here.</p>
      </div>
    );
  }
  else{
    return <></>;
  }
};
```

