### Retrieve Active Tooltip Data Points in Recharts (React)

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/API/hooks/useActiveTooltipDataPoints.mdx

This code snippet demonstrates how to use the `useActiveTooltipDataPoints` hook within a functional React component. It shows the basic import and invocation of the hook to get an array of data points active in the chart's tooltip, or `undefined` if no tooltip interaction is occurring.

```jsx
import { useActiveTooltipDataPoints } from 'recharts';

function MyChart() {
  const dataPoints = useActiveTooltipDataPoints();
}
```

